{"word":"G3845 - παραβαίνω - parabaínō - par-ab-ah'-ee-no - Transgress","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραβαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parabaínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ab-ah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Transgress</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இழந்துபோ, மீறிநட"},{"paragraph":"to go by the side of"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G939 - βάσις - básis - bas'-ece/939\">G939</a>; to <i>go contrary to</i>, that is, <i>violate</i> a command: - (by) transgress (-ion).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3845/3845\">G3845</a>, <a href=\"#/G3847/3847\">G3847</a>, <a href=\"#/G3848/3848\">G3848</a>, <a href=\"#/G5233/5233\">G5233</a>, <a href=\"#/G531/531\">G531</a>"}]}